LIBLIST=DAM DAMreader DiskBuffer DiskBufferReader DiskItem DiskItemReader DiskMultiItem DiskMultiItemReader DiskContentReader DocNameLookup DocumentTFGenerator IndexBuilderBase IndexBuilder IndexReaderBase InvertIndexBuilder InvertIndexReader Parser PForCompressor PForDecompressor porter PrefixTree PrefixTreeBuilder PrefixTreeMix PrefixTreeReader TermMeta TermNameLookup NameLookup NameLookupReader VectorInfo VectorInfoReader
INC=./include
SRCPATH=./src
LIBPATH=./lib

CXX=g++
CXXFLAGS = -O3 -I$(INC) -c
CPPLDFLAGS = -lz -lpthread -lm

all:
	for ITEM in  $(LIBLIST) ; do \
		echo "$(CXX) $(CXXFLAGS) $(SRCPATH)/$${ITEM}.cpp -o $(LIBPATH)/$${ITEM}.o" ; \
		$(CXX) $(CXXFLAGS) $(SRCPATH)/$${ITEM}.cpp -o $(LIBPATH)/$${ITEM}.o ; \
	done ;

clean:
	for ITEM in $(LIBLIST) ; do \
		rm -f $(LIBPATH)/$${ITEM}.o ; \
	done ;

